Mutane 832 sun mutu a ambaliyar tsunami a Indonesia
Rahoton da hukumar kula da bala'i ta kasar ta fitar a ranar Lahadi ya ce, adadin wadanda girgizar kasa da tsunami suka kashe a Indonesia ya kai 832.
Wani mai magana da yawun hukumar, Sutopo Purwo Nugroho ya shaidawa manema labarai cewa, girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 da ta auku a ranar Juma'a da kuma igiyar ruwa mai tsawon mita 6 da ta biyo baya, ta yi sanadiyar binne mutane da dama a karkashin tarkon.
An rufe titunan Palu da ke da mutane fiye da 380,000 da rushewar gine-gine.
