Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron Brett Kavanaugh
An samu fiye da mutane miliyan 20 a tashoshin talabijin guda shida domin sauraron shaidar da mai neman zama babban alkalin kotun tarayya, Brett Kavanaugh da matar da ta zarge shi da aikata fyade a shekarun 1980 mai suna Christine Blasey Ford.
A halin yanzu, ba a warware matsalar siyasa ba, kuma an dakatar da masu watsa shirye-shirye daga gudanar da shirye-shirye na yau da kullum saboda wani abin da ya faru a ranar Juma'a, lokacin da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi magana da cewa an ba FBI mako guda don bincika tuhumar.
Ford ya shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa yana da tabbacin cewa Kavanaugh ya yi masa fyade a wani biki a makarantar sakandare kuma ya yi kokarin cire tufafinsa.
Kavanaugh ya bayyana a shaidar da ya bayar cewa yana da tabbacin cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Masu kallo sun fi miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta ba da rahoton cewa sun ga shaidar a ranar Juma'a.
Nielsen ya yi lissafi ne ta hanyar kallon CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Lambar sauran tashoshin da suka watsa sauraron, kamar su PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network ba su kasance a bayyane ba.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen tana da wahalar auna yawan mutanen da suke kallon shirye-shiryen a wurin aikinsu.
Idan za a gwada, wannan shi ne yawan masu kallo da ake samu a wurin taron ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma wajen gabatar da kyautar Oscar.
A cewar Nielsen, Fox News Channel, wanda ya tara masu goyon bayan Kavanaugh, shi ne ya fi kowa kallon shi, inda ya kai miliyan 5.69 a duk lokacin da aka yi masa tambayoyi.
ABC ce ta biyu da ke kallon fina-finai da miliyan 3.26
CBS ya samu kallo miliyan uku, NBC ya samu 2.94, MSNBC ya samu 2.89, yayin da CNN ta samu kallo miliyan 2.52, a cewar rahoton Nielsen.
Ba a rage sha'awar ba bayan an yi hira.
Babban jarumin wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a shi ne Sanata Flake.
Bayan da ofishin Sanata mai ra'ayin mazan jiya ya fitar da sanarwar cewa zai kada kuri'a a kan Kavanaugh, an nuna shi a CNN da CBS a safiyar Juma'a, inda masu zanga-zanga suka yi masa maraba yayin da yake hawa kan lif don ya je wurin taron kwamitin shari'a.
Ya tsaya a tsaye yana kallon jama'a suna yi masa ba'a, kuma CNN ta watsa shi kai tsaye.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", wata mata ta gaya wa Sanata.
 Shin kuna tsammanin Kavanaugh yana faɗin gaskiya a gaban jama'ar ƙasar? 
Waɗansu kuwa suka ce, "Kai, kana da ikon yin abin da mata da yawa ba su iya yi ba".
Flake ya ce kawai ofishinsa ya fitar da wata sanarwa, kuma kafin a rufe kofar lif, ya kara da cewa zai ba da jawabinsa a zaman majalisa.
Sa'o'i bayan haka, tashoshin watsa shirye-shiryen TV da na waya sun nuna shi a matsayin mai jefa kuri'a kan ko za a gabatar da takarar Kavanaugh a gaban majalisar dattawa.
Flake ya ce zai amince da hakan ne kawai idan FBI ta binciki zargin da ake yi wa dan takarar a mako mai zuwa, kamar yadda 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya yi imani da bukatar hakan ne bayan tattaunawa da abokinsa, Sanata Chris Coons, dan Democrat.
Flake ya yanke shawarar ne bayan tattaunawa da Coons da sauran sanatoci.
Flake ya yi amfani da ikonsa yadda ya kamata, saboda ya bayyana cewa ba tare da binciken ba, 'yan Republican ba za su sami kuri'un da suka dace don amincewa da takarar Kavanaugh ba.
Shugaba Trump ya kaddamar da bincike kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
