An yi wa Erdogan maraba iri-iri a birnin Cologne
An yi farin ciki da farin ciki a taron da shugabannin Turkiyya da Jamus suka yi a Berlin a safiyar ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Satumba.
Ranar karshe ce ta ziyarar Erdogan ta raba kan Jamus, da nufin inganta alakar da ke tsakanin mambobin kungiyar NATO.
Dangantaka tsakanin kasashen biyu ta yi muni saboda batutuwan da suka shafi 'yancin bil'adama, 'yancin latsa labarai da kuma membobin Tarayyar Turai na Turkiyya.
Daga nan Erdogan ya tafi Cologne domin bikin bude wani babban masallaci da aka gina.
Birnin Cologne na da al'ummar Turkawa mafi yawa a wajen Turkiyya.
'Yan sanda sun haramta taron mutane 25,000 a gaban masallacin saboda dalilai na tsaro, amma magoya bayan shugaban sun bayyana don ganin shugaban kasar Turkiyya.
A wani bangare kuma, daruruwan masu zanga-zangar adawa da Erdogan  ciki har da Kurdawa  sun nuna rashin jin dadinsu game da manufofin Erdoğan da kuma shawarar da gwamnatin Jamus ta yanke na karbar shugaban kasar.
Wannan zanga-zanga ta nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin shugaban kasar wanda wasu 'yan kasar Jamus masu asalin Turkiya ke yaba masa a matsayin jarumi, yayin da wasu ke ganin shi a matsayin mai mulkin kama karya.
