Wannan labarin daga littafinmu na ranar Lahadi da safe: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, daidai shekara 136 da ta shige... ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi, Johannes Wilhelm Hans Geiger a Jamus.
