Akwai wasu abubuwa masu kyau a cikin sabon fim din Johnny English.
Na so yadda Johnny English ya zo ya hau kan wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da ya saka rigar yaƙi na zamanin da, sai ya kai inda rotors suka yi ta faduwa a kan kwalkwali na ɗan lokaci.
Atkinson yana da kyau a cikin fim, amma ba'a da kyau a cikin fim, kuma ba'a da kyau a cikin fim, saboda a yau, manyan fina-finai kamar James Bond da kuma Mission Impossible suna da ƙarfin hali don amfani da kayan aikin.
Ina jin cewa fim din yana da ban dariya ga yara, kuma a gare ni, Johnny English na rashin nasara, ba shi da kwarewa da kuma basira kamar yadda Atkinson ya kawo a cikin fim din Mr. Bean.
Wannan fim ya soma ne da wani abu mai muhimmanci: Biritaniya tana cikin haɗari mai tsanani.
Wani dan damfara na yanar gizo ya shiga cikin wani babban asirin yanar gizo na hukumar leken asirin Birtaniya, kuma ya gano duk wani jami'in Birtaniya, wanda ya fi kowa tsoro shi ne wakili Kevin Eldon, wanda rashin alheri ya samu karamin matsayi a fim din.
Wannan zai iya zama ƙusa ta ƙarshe a cikin kabari na firaministan da ke da girman kai da rarrabuwa, wanda ya riga ya lalace a siyasa: Emma Thompson tana wasa da Theresa May, kuma tana fitar da komai daga halin da ba a rubuta shi ba.
Masu ba shi shawara a kan harkokin tsaro sun gaya masa cewa tun da yake sun gano duk wani ɗan leƙen asiri da ke aiki a wurin, dole ne ya ba da wani ɗan leƙen asiri da ya yi ritaya.
Wannan dan sandan da ya yi ritaya, ba shakka, ba wani ba ne sai Johnny English, wanda yake da hannu biyu, wanda tun lokacin da ya yi ritaya yana aiki a matsayin malami a wata babbar makaranta, amma ya bar darasi ya koya wa yara game da leken asiri.
An kai English zuwa Whitehall, inda ya sake saduwa da tsohon mai ɗaukar makamai, Bough, wanda yanzu Ben Miller ke wasa, a lokacin sanarwar gaggawa.
Bough ya yi aure tun daga lokacin, kuma ya auri kyaftin din jirgin ruwa wanda yake magana da kunnuwansa. Vicki Pepperdine ce ke taka rawar kyaftin din, wanda ya cancanci yin wasu ayyuka mafi kyau.
Sai kuma Batman da Robin, masu hannun biyu na hukumar tsaron kasa ta mai girma, suka sake shiga cikin aiki, kuma suka fuskanci Ophelia Bulletova, wacce kyakkyawa Olga Kurylenko ta buga, a matsayin matar da ta dace.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista yana samun karbuwa daga wani mai karfin hali na IT wanda ya yi ikirarin cewa zai iya magance matsalolin dijital na Burtaniya: sunansa Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun fara aikin su na 'yan wasa: suna ɓoye a matsayin masu hidimar, suna ƙona gidan cin abinci na Faransa, sannan a cikin rikice-rikice masu ban mamaki suna ɓoye kansu a cikin jirgin ruwan Volta mai tsada, kuma English ya fitar da jahannama ta zahiri lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin gano gidan Volta ta amfani da kayan VR.
Muna bukatar waɗannan tashoshin don mu kai ga ƙarshe, amma duk da cewa mun yi farin ciki da kuma juyayi, yana da ɗan ɗan ɗan ƙaramin fim na yara.
Sakamakon ya kasance mai matsakaici.
Kamar yadda yake a sauran fina-finai na Johnny English, ina da tambaya: Shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da ta dace da baiwarta?
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Birtaniya ta musanta cewa za ta fara aiki na kwana hudu a duk lokacin da take biyan ma'aikatanta albashin kwana biyar.
Jam'iyyar Jeremy Corbyn ta Labour tana aiki a kan wani shiri mai ban mamaki: gabatar da mako-mako na aiki na kwana hudu, duk da haka, ta hanyar da ma'aikata za su yi aiki na kwana biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta ce tana son ma'aikata su amfana daga juyin juya halin kere kere (AI) ta hanyar ba da karin hutu ga ma'aikata ta hanyar samun karin kudaden shiga.
A tsarin, ma'aikata za su samu hutun mako uku, kuma su dawo gida da adadin da suka saba samu.
Majiyoyin sun ce wannan ra'ayin zai dace da shirin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar, wanda ke nufin sanya ma'auni a kan bangaren ma'aikata a kasar.
Taron Kungiyoyin kwadago na kasar Sin ma sun goyi bayan wannan tsari na kwana hudu na aiki domin su ce hakan zai bai wa ma'aikata damar cin gajiyar sauyin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times cewa, "Za a sanar da sake duba manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
Ko da yake ba za ta faru ba da dare ba, amma ranar aiki ta kwana hudu wata dabara ce da ta dace da shirin jam'iyyar da zai sanya ma'aikata a matsayin masu daidaita tattalin arziki, kuma ya dace da dabarun masana'antu na jam'iyyar.
Ba jam'iyyar Labour ce ta farko da ta goyi bayan irin wannan ra'ayin ba, jam'iyyar Green Party ta riga ta yi yakin neman zabe a zaben majalisar dokoki na 2017 da alkawarin mako hudu.
Amma, ba a amince da wannan ra'ayin a jam'iyyar Labour ba.
Mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar ta Labour ya bayyana cewa: Ayyukan kwana hudu ba su cikin manufofin da jam'iyyar ke goyon baya, kuma batun ba ma kan ajanda ba.
A taron jam'iyyar Labour na makon da ya gabata, John McDonnell, mai kula da kudaden shiga ya bayyana ra'ayinsa na juyin juya halin zamantakewar tattalin arziki.
