Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da tallace-tallace na yaudara a kasar
Jakadan kasar Sin na Amurka ya zargi Beijing da yada farfaganda a jaridar Amurka, mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani sanarwa mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka, wanda ya jaddada fa'idodin alakar kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi nuni da wani talla da ya buga a jaridarsa mafi sayarwa a Iowa a ranar Laraba a jaridar China Daily Des Moines Register, inda ya zargi kasar Sin da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben da aka yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
Trump ya zargi Beijing da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, wasu jami'an Amurka sun shaida wa Reuters cewa wannan sabon mataki ne na kara tsanantawa da Washington ke yi wa China, da nufin matsa mata lamba.
Ko da yake ba sabon abu ba ne gwamnatocin ƙasashen waje su tallata kasuwanci da ƙasarsu, ana ƙara yin yaƙin kasuwanci tsakanin Beijing da Washington, inda suke saka ƙarin haraji a kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
Masana na Amurka da na kasar Sin sun ce, a farkon yakin cinikayya, harajin da kasar Sin ta saka a matsayin martani, ya yi niyya ne wajen kai wa masu fitar da kayayyaki daga jihohin da Trump da jam'iyyar Republican ke da rinjaye, kamar Iowa.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa mai shekaru da yawa ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa, saboda jihar Iowa tana fitar da kayayyakin gona da yawa zuwa China.
Branstad ya rubuta a cikin wani labarin da ya fito a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi cewa, "Kasar Sin ta ci gaba da cin zarafin kasarmu ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace a cikin jaridarmu mai 'yanci".
"Gwamnatin China ta yi amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da 'yancin latsawa ta hanyar yada farfaganda a cikin tallace-tallace da aka biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
 Idan ka je kantin sayar da jaridu a Beijing, ba za ka ga labarai masu ban haushi ba.  Jaridar kasar Sin ba ta nuna ra'ayoyin mutane daban-daban game da yanayin tattalin arzikin kasar Sin da ke kara tabarbarewa, domin kafofin watsa labarai suna karkashin kulawar jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin. 
