Mutane 384 ne suka rasa rayukansu a ranar Juma'a a lokacin da wata girgizar kasa mai karfin guguwa ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia, inda hukumomi ke ganin adadin wadanda suka mutu zai iya ƙaruwa.
Har ila yau, hanyoyin sadarwa na yankin sun lalace, don haka ba a samu wani labari ba daga lardin Donggala, arewacin Palut, inda girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5 ta afku.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga birnin Palu.
Wasu muhimman bayanai game da Pallu da Donggala a tsibirin Celebes:
Babban birnin lardin Palu na Tsakiya-Celebes, wanda aka gina a gefen yammacin tsibirin Celebes a ƙarshen bakin teku, yana da yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Ya yi bikin cika shekara 40 da kafa birnin sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa da kuma ambaliyar ruwa suka addabe shi.
Gwamnatin Donggala tana da nisan kilomita 300 a gabar arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Celebes.
A shekara ta 2017, yawan mutanen lardin  wanda ke da ƙananan hukumomi fiye da lardin  ya kai kimanin 299 200.
Tsakiyar Tsakiya ta tsakiya ta fi dacewa da kamun kifi da noma, musamman a yankunan Donggala na bakin teku.
Ma'adinan nickel wani muhimmin bangare ne na tattalin arziki, amma ya fi mayar da hankali a Morowali, a gefen gabar Celebes.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesiya ta ce a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi ambaliyar ruwa a birnin Palut da Donggala sau da yawa.
Ruwan sama da ya auku a shekara ta 1938 ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
A shekara ta 1996, ambaliyar ruwa ta kai yammacin Donggala, kuma mutane tara suka mutu.
Domin ƙasar Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake kira Ring of Fire a Tekun Fasifik, kuma tana yawan girgizar ƙasa.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da kuma ambaliyar ruwa da aka yi a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata babbar girgizar kasa ta barke a yammacin yankin Aceh na Arewacin Sumatra, ta haifar da ambaliyar ruwa da ta kai kasashe 14, ta kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin wadanda suka mutu a Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
A tsibirin Nias, kusa da Sumatra, mutane da yawa sun mutu.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta girgiza kudancin tsibirin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesiya, kuma ambaliyar ruwa da ta biyo baya ta kashe mutane kusan 700 a gaɓar kudu.
2009: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.6 ta yi ambaliya a kusa da Padang, babban birnin lardin yammacin Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka rasa rayukansu.
2010: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta girgiza tsibirin Mentawai kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo girgizar ruwa mai tsawon mita 10 a wasu wurare, ta halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ta kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa da ta afkawa Aceh Pidie Jaya, ta haifar da fargaba da kuma bala'i, wanda ya tunatar da mutane da dama game da mummunan ambaliyar da ta auku a shekarar 2004.
Ba a yi ruwan sama ba, amma har yanzu fiye da mutane 100 sun mutu a ƙarƙashin gine-ginen da suka rushe.
2018: Lombok, tsibiri ne da ya shahara a Indonesiya, inda girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta kashe mutane 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Dubban gine-gine sun rushe kuma dubban masu yawon bude ido sun makale a tsibirin na ɗan lokaci.
