Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta doke tawagar Amurka da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Gold National da aka yi a wajen Paris.
Wannan shi ne karo na shida da Amurka ta yi rashin nasara a gasar Turai, kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta kare kofin gasar ne, yayin da tawagar Thomas Bjørn ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin kayar da Amurka.
Phil Mickelson, dan wasan Amurka wanda ya yi fama da dukan wasan, ya jefa kwallo a cikin ruwa a kan rami na 16 na par-3 don ya ba da nasara ga Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya Molinari ya yi fice a dukkan fannoni, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka taba cin nasara 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Jordan Spieth na Amurka ya yi nasara da 5&4 a kan dan wasan da ya fi kasa a rukunin Turai, Thorbjørn Olesen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasan duniya, ya ci 2 da 1 a kan dan Ingila Ian Poulter, wanda zai iya kasancewa a gasar Ryder ta karshe.
Tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup takwas, Sergio Garcia na Spain ya zama babban dan wasan Turai na gasar cin kofin duniya da ya samu maki 25.5 a wasan.
