Ya mika kyautar ga Jon Rahm wanda ya doke Tiger Woods a wasan daya da biyu a ranar Lahadi.
"Ina alfahari sosai da na doke Tiger Woods, na girma ina kallon wannan mutumin", in ji Rahm, mai shekara 23.
Woods ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa, kuma yanzu yana da tarihin 13-21-3 a gasar Ryder.
Wannan wani adadi ne mai ban mamaki daga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasan da suka taba lashe kofuna 14 a duniya, wanda Jack Nicklaus ne kawai ya fi shi.
