Labaran Red Wave: Rashin yawan mutane a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani rahoto da hukumar kifi da namun daji ta Florida ta fitar ya nuna cewa, a wasu yankunan Tampa Bay, an samu raguwar yawan ruwan sama mai ruwan sama.
FWC ta ce an samu karin fure a yankin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma Collier, wanda ke nuna raguwar yawan.
Wannan jan ruwa ya kai kusan mil 130 daga yankin Pinellas da ke arewa zuwa Lee County da ke kudu.
Akwai tabo a wajen mil 10 daga yankin Hillsborough County, amma a kan karamin yanki idan aka kwatanta da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma samu wani yanayi mai zafi a yankin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an samu matsakaicin taro a Pinellas County da kewayen tekun, matsakaicin taro a kan iyakar Hillsborough County, matsakaicin taro a Manatee County, matsakaicin taro a kan iyakar Sarasota County da kewayen tekun, matsakaicin taro a kan iyakar Charlotte County, matsakaicin taro a kan iyakar Lee County da kewayen tekun, da kuma matsakaicin taro a kan iyakar Collier County.
Rahotanni na ci gaba da zuwa game da ciwon numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da kuma Collier.
Ba a samu rahoton ciwon numfashi a makon da ya gabata daga arewa maso yammacin Florida.
